title: Tommy is Back, BET The Bobby Brown Story, Nike, Voter Talk, Humpday Confessions, Show Close and more.
itunes:title: Tommy is Back, BET The Bobby Brown Story, Nike, Voter Talk, Humpday Confessions, Show Close and more.
description:
Fool #1 is back. The 2 Fools talk about their weekend. The Bobby Brown Story is making waves. Nike has the entire country talking with its controversial ad featuring Colin Kaepernick. Humpday Confessions with Nephew Tommy is here. The booth is officially open. The show speaks to us about the importance of voting just before it wraps up and more.
